  "description": {
    "zh": "是的，我确实有点事需要处理。你看，现在消息已经传开了，特工先生。你的雇主已经提前通知了我，说你很快会来找我。我还在想你什么时候出现呢！既然你现在来了，那就说正事吧。\n\nUSEC 的介入实在令人头疼，我们确实没什么办法能摆脱他们……\n但也不是没有办法，你明白我的意思吧？我想你可以做点事——希望你愿意听我细说。\n\n你可以去干掉几个 USEC，但前提是——你得看起来就像是他们自己人，明白吗？别误会，我可不是很支持你干这事，我可是有客户要照顾的，而那些“游客”往往是最舍得花钱的！所以别指望这次有什么酬劳，明白了？\n\n不过我倒是可以帮你和你那位朋友搞的行动，只是我也需要点东西，不是什么稀奇要求——就点燃料。等你凑够几个油箱就给我带来，最好是体积小点的那种。我不会和别人提起这些事，那些货也会被好好藏起来，我发誓守口如瓶。怎么样，干不干？\n\nUSEC装备 要求：\n - 任意 HighCom Striker头盔款式 或 Ballistic Armor Co. Bastion头盔款式 或 USEC棒球帽款式\n - HighCom Trooper TFO 防弹背心 或 Interceptor OTV防弹衣 / MBSS背包 / 5.11 TacTec插板胸挂\n - 任意 北约枪支武器",
    "en": "Yes there is something, actually. You see, word got around, mister operator. Your employer already informed me about your little operation, told me to expect you anytime, I was wondering when you would show up! But now you're here, so let's talk business.\n\nUSEC involvement is annoying, can't do much about it...\nBut there are methods, you know? I think I know what you could do - I hope you're all ears!\n\nYou could take out some USECs, but you need to be looking like one of them, clear as day! What do you think? But don't think I support this too much, I got customers after all, and those tourists get to pay the most! So don't expect some sort of payment after you completed your task, understand?\n\nI can help you two out with that operation that is going on right now, but I need a favor, nothing too wild, just some fuel. Bring it to me whenever you got enough, a few canisters should do fine, make sure to bring compact ones. And don't worry, I won't talk about it with anyone, those shipments will stay hidden for now, my lips are sealed, got it? So, are you in or out?\n\nUSEC Gear :\n - Any HighCom Striker Helmet / Ballistic Armor Co. Bastion Helmet / USEC Cap\n - HighCom Trooper TFO / Interceptor OTV / MBSS / 5.11 TacTec\n - Any Western-Made Firearm"
  },
